8
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:56,150
Got that.

9
00:01:57,990 --> 00:01:58,650
Examining.

10
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:02,710
There're scratches on his left arm and the back of his left hand.

11
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,400
There're bruises on his left upper arm.

12
00:02:08,870 --> 00:02:09,530
Examining.

13
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:12,010
There're huge bruises

14
00:02:12,050 --> 00:02:14,150
on the victim's right arm and right wrist.

15
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,190
There are scratches

16
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,120
on his right arm.

17
00:02:25,070 --> 00:02:25,730
Examining.

18
00:02:26,190 --> 00:02:28,950
The victim was stabbed in the back with a blade.

19
00:02:30,230 --> 00:02:30,870
Got that.

20
00:02:33,670 --> 00:02:35,430
There're wounds on his chest.

21
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,160
Both front and back.

22
00:02:37,670 --> 00:02:39,829
The skin around the wounds is largely wrinkled and bulging.

23
00:02:39,829 --> 00:02:42,280
The blood stains around are coagulated.

24
00:02:43,140 --> 00:02:43,790
Got that.

25
00:02:45,829 --> 00:02:47,140
There's also a tear

26
00:02:47,670 --> 00:02:48,710
on the robe.

27
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:52,240
It's the same kind as the wound on the body,

28
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:55,000
and there are blood stains both inside and out.

29
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:58,030
So the preliminary determination is that

30
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,880
he was stabbed by a sharp weapon

31
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:01,840
in the back,

32
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:03,670
which pierced through his body

33
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:05,130
and stuck out of his chest.

34
00:03:05,670 --> 00:03:08,270
This is the fatal wound.

35
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:12,990
Judged by the wound, the time of death should be

36
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,270
9 p.m. the day before yesterday.

37
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:20,440
You even figured that out?

38
00:03:21,070 --> 00:03:21,670
Got that.

39
00:03:22,190 --> 00:03:23,470
Postmortem is over.

40
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:25,390
Mother.

41
00:03:29,510 --> 00:03:32,150
Isn't there another body over there?

42
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:36,470
Mother, don't overwork.

43
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:38,280
By the way,

44
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:42,030
where is my son Dugu Yang?

45
00:03:42,350 --> 00:03:43,910
He has become a coroner.

46
00:03:44,550 --> 00:03:46,150
Get him to do the postmortem,

47
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:48,850
and I'll assist him from the side.

48
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:49,790
Mother.

49
00:03:50,550 --> 00:03:51,350
Dugu Yang...

50
00:03:51,829 --> 00:03:52,390
He...

51
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:57,990
Why are you stammering?

52
00:03:58,020 --> 00:03:59,650
Are you covering up for him?

53
00:04:00,110 --> 00:04:01,240
A murder took place.

54
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,040
As a coroner,

55
00:04:03,070 --> 00:04:04,470
he still hasn't arrived.

56
00:04:04,980 --> 00:04:07,150
How can he live up to the trust

57
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:09,230
of the criminal-catching officers and the government office?

58
00:04:09,230 --> 00:04:11,190
How can he live up to

59
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:13,460
the victim and his family's expectations?

60
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:14,550
I knew it.

61
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:16,250
She had a panic attack.

62
00:04:16,269 --> 00:04:18,420
Can the postmortem performed in this mental state

63
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:19,470
count?

64
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:20,470
Chuntiao.

65
00:04:20,670 --> 00:04:22,029
Take your mother home.

66
00:04:22,350 --> 00:04:22,820
Tell her

67
00:04:22,990 --> 00:04:24,030
Dugu Yang is dead.

68
00:04:24,230 --> 00:04:25,670
She did his postmortem herself yesterday.

69
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:26,470
Assistant Xu.

70
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:37,040
[Lingdu Burial Goods Store]

71
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:46,270
I forgot.

72
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:49,909
My son

73
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:54,170
is dead.

74
00:05:07,110 --> 00:05:10,430
I, Cao Hui, the female coroner of Tang, am here to examine the body.

75
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:12,630
Irrelevant people, stay clear.

76
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:14,750
Mother.

77
00:05:15,030 --> 00:05:16,290
Why are you nagging me?

78
00:05:16,870 --> 00:05:17,390
Mother.

79
00:05:18,090 --> 00:05:19,090
Let's go home

80
00:05:19,110 --> 00:05:20,160
and have a rest.

81
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:22,150
How about we examine the other body tomorrow?

82
00:05:22,150 --> 00:05:23,470
Postmortem is a matter of

83
00:05:23,470 --> 00:05:24,950
the truth of death

84
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:26,350
and the justice in the world.

85
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:29,350
As a coroner, how can I slack off?

86
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:36,190
Don't worry. I'm here.

87
00:05:38,990 --> 00:05:39,650
Examining.

88
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:41,550
The victim's head is intact.

89
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:43,870
There are no signs of poisoning.

90
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,560
Her eyes are bulging.

91
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:48,650
His tongue is, too.

92
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:51,210
His hands are slightly clenched.

93
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:53,090
There's bleeding in his nose.

94
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:55,510
There're huge bruises and scratches

95
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:56,420
on his neck.

96
00:05:56,990 --> 00:05:59,320
It seems that he was tussling with someone

97
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:01,750
and got choked by the throat before he died.

98
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:02,350
Got that.

99
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:06,950
Mother.

100
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:08,070
Mother.

101
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:08,840
Don't panic!

102
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:09,870
Give us a hand!

103
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,990
Carry her into the room.

104
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:11,390
Mother.

105
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:11,830
Come on.

106
00:06:11,830 --> 00:06:12,110
Okay.

107
00:06:12,110 --> 00:06:12,510
Hurry.

108
00:06:14,550 --> 00:06:14,990
Go.

109
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:15,890
Who is this?

110
00:06:15,910 --> 00:06:17,440
I've never seen him before.

111
00:06:17,590 --> 00:06:18,520
I don't know him.

112
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:22,590
Er!

113
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:23,990
Er!

114
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:26,230
Er!

115
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:27,550
My brother!

116
00:06:27,790 --> 00:06:29,520
My brother!

117
00:06:29,700 --> 00:06:30,510
Er!

118
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,740
The victim's identity is confirmed

119
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:33,140
to be Lu Er, a tomb robber.

120
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,790
The conclusion of the postmortem just now

121
00:06:34,790 --> 00:06:35,990
is also consistent with what Chunshan said.

122
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:37,700
Er!

123
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:39,870
Er!

124
00:06:41,290 --> 00:06:42,370
-Er!
-Go.

125
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:44,040
-Go.
-Er!

126
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,030
My brother.

127
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:47,020
-Go.
-Er!

128
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:50,070
Er!

129
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:53,840
There's no obvious injury

130
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:55,470
other than the one on his neck.

131
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:56,930
He was strangled to death.

132
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:02,910
Take the body back to the government office first.

133
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:07,550
You...

134
00:07:23,990 --> 00:07:25,230
Excuse me. Make way.

135
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:28,370
Give me two.

136
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:29,150
Okay.

137
00:07:32,550 --> 00:07:33,750
Miss, buy one please.

138
00:07:33,909 --> 00:07:34,510
Let me see.

139
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:35,630
-Make way.
-Okay.

140
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:37,230
Mr. Ma.

141
00:07:38,140 --> 00:07:39,470
I’ll go buy some naans stuffed with lamb

142
00:07:39,470 --> 00:07:40,670
from your shop later.

143
00:07:40,740 --> 00:07:42,140
My youngest son loves it.

144
00:07:42,550 --> 00:07:44,710
Good. It's good that you like it.

145
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,480
Take a look.

146
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:52,659
[Ma's Naan Shop]

147
00:07:50,790 --> 00:07:51,790
You've finished?

148
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:52,390
Yes.

149
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,150
Come again.

150
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:54,310
Okay, thank you.

151
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:54,960
See you.

152
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:56,550
Take care.

153
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:58,820
Boss, you're back.

154
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:01,470
Ask everyone to come out.

155
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:04,590
Wait.

156
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:07,750
And all the shopkeepers of each branch,

157
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:08,750
and all the staff.

158
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,360
Call all of them over.

159
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:11,750
Okay.

160
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:15,830
Someone is recuperating in the room.

161
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:16,760
Don't be afraid.

162
00:08:22,470 --> 00:08:23,270
You're awake.

163
00:08:23,990 --> 00:08:24,430
Let me.

164
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:30,970
Be careful.

165
00:08:33,659 --> 00:08:34,390
Xijun.

166
00:08:35,150 --> 00:08:36,080
It's really you.

167
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:38,990
I was dizzy,

168
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,520
and I think I saw you and Chicken Fed.

169
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:43,350
I thought

170
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:47,110
it was a dream on my way to Bridge of Helplessness.

171
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:52,430
How is he?

172
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:56,590
He was also injured by a hidden weapon, I remember.

173
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:58,290
Is he alive or dead?

174
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:00,350
He's fine.

175
00:09:01,350 --> 00:09:03,630
He's just still unconscious.

176
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,810
I'd rather see him dead.

177
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:15,230
What's wrong?

178
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,270
Are you hungry?

179
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:23,330
She's asking you to

180
00:09:23,350 --> 00:09:25,430
seek justice for her father and her older brother.

181
00:09:25,430 --> 00:09:27,350
You understand what she says?

182
00:09:28,860 --> 00:09:30,420
How can I make my way in this world

183
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,680
if I can't even do that?

184
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:33,950
Great.

185
00:09:35,630 --> 00:09:36,350
Young lady.

186
00:09:36,990 --> 00:09:38,850
I know your older brother is dead.

187
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:39,990
But why

188
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,830
was his body discovered in a clay figurine?

189
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:43,160
What exactly happened?

190
00:09:43,390 --> 00:09:44,590
Tell her everything.

191
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,520
Naans stuffed with lamb!

192
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:52,710
Our boss's treat!

193
00:09:52,820 --> 00:09:55,080
Free for all the people of Shiyang to try.

194
00:09:55,350 --> 00:09:56,270
Come on, there's enough for everyone.

195
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:57,550
You can all have it. Don't push.

196
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,350
Here you go.

197
00:09:58,470 --> 00:09:59,870
Come on. Don't push.

198
00:09:59,990 --> 00:10:00,950
Here you go.

199
00:10:00,950 --> 00:10:02,510
Give me one. Give me one.

200
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,750
This naan is really delicious.

201
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,550
How much is it?

202
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,440
It's free.

203
00:10:11,990 --> 00:10:12,710
Ma Huai

204
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:14,830
asked his staff to give away naans for free in the streets.

205
00:10:14,830 --> 00:10:15,430
And he said

206
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,970
this would go on for 3 days.

207
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,950
Magistrate, try it.

208
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:22,130
Are his naans hard to sell?

209
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,120
They're not.

210
00:10:23,390 --> 00:10:24,750
Since Ma Huai returned to Shiyang

211
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:25,910
and opened his naan shop,

212
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:26,640
his business

213
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,710
has been thriving.

214
00:10:34,470 --> 00:10:35,870
The victim, Lou Qingtai,

215
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:38,030
once suspected his father Lou Lide

216
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:39,230
was poisoned to death

217
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:40,380
by this naan.

218
00:10:46,810 --> 00:10:48,870
You don't think Ma Huai could have...

219
00:10:49,310 --> 00:10:50,120
Lu Lingfeng.

220
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:53,150
I did these two rough sketches

221
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:53,870
according to

222
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:55,230
Lou Qingtai's sister's

223
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:56,130
statement.

224
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:57,070
Take a look

225
00:10:57,230 --> 00:10:59,230
and see if it can help solve the case.

226
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:13,350
Ms. Pei.

227
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:15,140
Qingniao is a mute,

228
00:11:15,390 --> 00:11:16,080
yet you managed to guess

229
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,380
what she wanted to say

230
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:18,750
and drew it.

231
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:20,480
You're a genius.

232
00:11:20,670 --> 00:11:21,400
That's true.

233
00:11:21,780 --> 00:11:23,260
Ms. Pei is indeed a genius.

234
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:25,480
Back when we were in Nanzhou...

235
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:31,210
Who's beating the Admonishment Drum?

236
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:39,610
Ma Huai, why are you beating the drum?

237
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:40,830
This drum is for

238
00:11:40,850 --> 00:11:42,110
those who have grievances to report.

239
00:11:42,110 --> 00:11:42,550
You...

240
00:11:48,230 --> 00:11:49,230
I killed someone.

241
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,430
I killed Lou Qingtai.

242
00:11:53,430 --> 00:11:54,290
I plead guilty.

243
00:12:01,140 --> 00:12:01,990
That night,

244
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:09,590
I was going to deliver

245
00:12:09,590 --> 00:12:10,590
clay to Dugu Yang.

246
00:12:11,950 --> 00:12:12,910
Right after I moved all the clay

247
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:13,710
into the yard,

248
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:15,470
Lou Qingtai came.

249
00:12:19,630 --> 00:12:20,310
You...

250
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,050
Why are you here?

251
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:24,270
Are you here to get even with Dugu Yang?

252
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:24,670
Yes.

253
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:25,710
He's not here.

254
00:12:26,140 --> 00:12:26,550
You...

255
00:12:27,870 --> 00:12:29,600
I'll get even with you instead.

256
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:31,310
I told you

257
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,020
your father did like

258
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:33,860
my naans,

259
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,750
but his death has nothing to do with me.

260
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:36,750
Nothing?

261
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:39,220
Then why did you bribe Dugu Yang,

262
00:12:39,350 --> 00:12:40,750
even with silver ingots?

263
00:12:42,090 --> 00:12:43,350
What are you doing now?

264
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:45,390
You're such a rich shop owner.

265
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:46,990
Why do you work for Dugu Yang?

266
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:50,010
It's obvious that you colluded with him,

267
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,210
and he helped you conceal your crime

268
00:12:51,210 --> 00:12:52,620
of poisoning my father.

269
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:54,350
I didn't poison your father.

270
00:12:54,350 --> 00:12:56,310
And I won't let you slander Coroner Dugu.

271
00:12:56,310 --> 00:12:56,790
Go away!

272
00:12:58,550 --> 00:12:59,280
Lou Qingtai.

273
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:01,000
You can't slander me,

274
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:03,190
and you can't slander Coroner Dugu.

275
00:13:37,830 --> 00:13:38,760
After I got home,

276
00:13:39,310 --> 00:13:41,200
the more I thought about it, the more scared I got.

277
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,470
I was worried that Lou Qingtai

278
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:44,530
would hold this against Coroner Dugu

279
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:47,120
and come back to avenge him when he got home.

280
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,750
So I went back.

281
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:50,890
I didn't expect

282
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:54,200
that Lou Qingtai was already dead.

283
00:13:56,950 --> 00:13:59,210
I committed involuntary manslaughter.

284
00:14:00,950 --> 00:14:02,410
I was filled with remorse,

285
00:14:04,470 --> 00:14:05,530
but it was too late.

286
00:14:08,510 --> 00:14:10,370
I was afraid of being discovered,

287
00:14:11,870 --> 00:14:12,830
so I hid the body

288
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:15,470
in a clay figurine.

289
00:14:35,070 --> 00:14:36,350
I was worried someone would see me,

290
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:36,890
so I left

291
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:38,710
with the clay figurine half-done.

292
00:14:38,710 --> 00:14:40,240
I, Ma Huai, am the murderer.

293
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:42,010
There's nothing to deny here.

294
00:14:42,590 --> 00:14:44,950
I'll accept it even if I have to pay with my life.

295
00:14:44,950 --> 00:14:45,880
Unfortunately,

296
00:14:47,470 --> 00:14:48,870
Lou Lide is dead.

297
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:52,390
I can't be beheaded

298
00:14:54,110 --> 00:14:56,240
by the same executioner as my parents.

299
00:15:03,470 --> 00:15:04,670
How dare you, Ma Huai!

300
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:06,830
Did you poison Lou Lide to death?

301
00:15:07,390 --> 00:15:08,190
Of course not.

302
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:09,760
I only use fresh lamb

303
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:10,830
in my naans.

304
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:14,250
I use a variety of seasonings to make them taste delicious,

305
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:15,780
but they're not poisonous.

306
00:15:15,830 --> 00:15:16,630
Then why did you

307
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:17,720
bribe Dugu Yang?

308
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:20,190
What do you mean I bribed him?

309
00:15:24,650 --> 00:15:25,690
Look what this is.

310
00:15:40,350 --> 00:15:41,320
Who drew this?

311
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:44,870
It does look like us.

312
00:15:44,990 --> 00:15:45,960
So you admit it?

313
00:15:46,190 --> 00:15:46,850
No, I don't.

314
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:47,510
You don't?

315
00:15:48,350 --> 00:15:49,350
We have a witness.

316
00:15:49,430 --> 00:15:50,780
Lou Lide's daughter Qingniao

317
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:52,110
saw it with her own eyes.

318
00:15:52,230 --> 00:15:53,550
If you take advantage of her being a mute

319
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:54,510
and refuse to confess,

320
00:15:54,510 --> 00:15:56,190
you'll be tortured.

321
00:15:57,380 --> 00:15:57,870
I admit that

322
00:15:57,870 --> 00:15:59,670
I did give Coroner Dugu some silver ingots,

323
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:01,070
but that wasn't bribery.

324
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:02,920
I won't allow you

325
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,850
to tarnish my mentor's innocence.

326
00:16:05,470 --> 00:16:06,070
Mentor?

327
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,360
Were you learning

328
00:16:08,710 --> 00:16:09,750
how to make clay figurines that keep tomb robbers away

329
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:11,600
from him?

330
00:16:13,310 --> 00:16:15,440
This has nothing to do with my killing.

331
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:17,300
I don't want to talk about it.

332
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:18,310
When you left the backyard

333
00:16:18,310 --> 00:16:19,740
of the burial goods store for the first time,

334
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:21,540
did you see Lou Qingtai was dead?

335
00:16:22,750 --> 00:16:23,270
No.

336
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:25,470
Did his eyes bulge?

337
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:27,250
And what about his tongue?

338
00:16:27,990 --> 00:16:28,470
Well...

339
00:16:29,510 --> 00:16:30,510
I can't remember.

340
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:33,270
What about his hands?

341
00:16:34,290 --> 00:16:36,090
He seemed to be pinching his neck

342
00:16:37,510 --> 00:16:40,110
with his hands in an attempt to breathe better.

343
00:16:46,070 --> 00:16:47,550
Lu Da's younger brother.

344
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:51,110
Qingniao's older brother.

345
00:16:58,780 --> 00:17:00,270
So Qingniao's older brother

346
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:01,400
that Mr. Su murmured

347
00:17:01,590 --> 00:17:02,710
is Lou Qingtai.

348
00:17:03,790 --> 00:17:04,869
Lu Da's younger brother

349
00:17:04,869 --> 00:17:05,819
is Lu Er.

350
00:17:06,550 --> 00:17:07,780
Although he's still unconscious,

351
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:08,390
he managed to name

352
00:17:08,390 --> 00:17:09,670
the two bodies.

353
00:17:10,190 --> 00:17:12,550
He's indeed a genius.

354
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,150
Unfortunately, he's still in a coma

355
00:17:16,150 --> 00:17:17,310
and can't perform postmortem.

356
00:17:17,310 --> 00:17:18,770
I don't think he can wake up

357
00:17:18,829 --> 00:17:19,569
in a few days.

358
00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:21,790
We should ask a coroner from a nearby county

359
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:23,030
to assist in the postmortem.

360
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:24,390
Why do we need another coroner?

361
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:25,050
Haven't all three bodies

362
00:17:25,050 --> 00:17:26,380
already been examined?

363
00:17:28,030 --> 00:17:29,790
Cao Hui is a competent coroner.

364
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,740
But due to her illness,

365
00:17:31,870 --> 00:17:33,710
she didn't complete the postmortem.

366
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:34,310
Besides,

367
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,150
according to the current statement

368
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:37,750
and the postmortem results,

369
00:17:38,590 --> 00:17:40,190
Lu Er was killed by Dugu Yang,

370
00:17:40,670 --> 00:17:42,830
and Lou Qingtai was killed by Ma Huai.

371
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:45,510
But there's no clue

372
00:17:46,190 --> 00:17:47,650
as to who killed Dugu Yang.

373
00:17:47,710 --> 00:17:49,470
Regarding the murderer of Dugu Yang,

374
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:50,270
I have 3 suspects

375
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:51,630
in my mind.

376
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:52,840
Go ahead.

377
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:55,290
The first one is Chunshan.

378
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:57,050
He's the most suspicious.

379
00:18:04,670 --> 00:18:05,550
Where is the seal?

380
00:18:05,550 --> 00:18:07,190
There's no seal at all.

381
00:18:07,630 --> 00:18:08,880
Take the 10 taels of silver here

382
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,340
and leave Shiyang County.

383
00:18:10,550 --> 00:18:11,960
Never come back again.

384
00:18:18,150 --> 00:18:18,950
Dugu Yang.

385
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:21,040
You own such a precious seal,

386
00:18:21,070 --> 00:18:23,430
yet you made my sister live in poverty with you.

387
00:18:23,430 --> 00:18:25,580
I haven't said anything in so many years.

388
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:27,480
Now you want me to cover up the fact that you committed murder

389
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:29,140
just with some silver ingots?

390
00:18:29,630 --> 00:18:31,230
Do I look like a beggar to you?

391
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:32,510
Shameless!

392
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:35,300
You're even worse than a beggar.

393
00:18:35,870 --> 00:18:36,750
Get lost!

394
00:18:38,870 --> 00:18:39,470
Dugu Yang.

395
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:44,390
If you don't give me the seal,

396
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:45,880
I'll look for it myself.

397
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,150
But in the end,

398
00:18:47,470 --> 00:18:49,190
Chunshan didn't find Dugu Xin Multifaceted Seal

399
00:18:49,190 --> 00:18:50,590
in the burial goods store.

400
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:51,910
After that, he escaped from Shiyang

401
00:18:51,910 --> 00:18:54,190
and took part in treasure gambling in Qingchuan Town,

402
00:18:54,190 --> 00:18:55,520
where he met General Lu.

403
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,790
Then, he sneaked back

404
00:18:56,790 --> 00:18:58,540
to Dugu Yang's house

405
00:18:58,590 --> 00:19:00,320
in an attempt to steal the seal.

406
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:02,450
Your analysis is reasonable.

407
00:19:03,270 --> 00:19:05,190
But when did Chunshan admit he killed Dugu Yang?

408
00:19:05,190 --> 00:19:06,450
Where is the evidence?

409
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:07,960
Well...

410
00:19:08,150 --> 00:19:09,210
I don't have it now.

411
00:19:09,950 --> 00:19:11,990
But I'm afraid

412
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:14,670
torture is the only way we can deal with such a shameless person.

413
00:19:14,670 --> 00:19:15,270
Continue.

414
00:19:16,670 --> 00:19:18,030
The second suspect

415
00:19:18,430 --> 00:19:19,270
is Dong Haogu.

416
00:19:20,110 --> 00:19:21,770
I didn't report it to the court

417
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:24,390
because I didn’t want to get myself suspected.

418
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:25,830
Since he didn't get the seal,

419
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:26,510
Dong Haogu

420
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,610
first seduced a married woman,

421
00:19:28,860 --> 00:19:29,710
and then tried to take advantage of

422
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:30,910
that rat, Chunshan.

423
00:19:31,630 --> 00:19:33,230
How can we believe his words?

424
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:34,150
I think

425
00:19:34,630 --> 00:19:35,830
this is what happened

426
00:19:36,190 --> 00:19:37,830
on that night.

427
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:45,110
This seal is an ancestral inheritance of my family.

428
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:47,840
Please take good care of it.

429
00:19:48,150 --> 00:19:49,720
Don't do it wrong.

430
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:51,670
No problem.

431
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:56,070
Dugu Yang.

432
00:19:57,710 --> 00:19:58,490
Do you really think

433
00:19:58,490 --> 00:20:00,150
I'm doing business with you?

434
00:20:00,590 --> 00:20:01,740
I love the seal,

435
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,030
but I love money more.

436
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:09,590
After Dong Haogu got the seal,

437
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:12,290
he didn't escape from Shiyang immediately.

438
00:20:14,990 --> 00:20:16,180
On the one hand, he didn't want to give himself away.

439
00:20:16,180 --> 00:20:16,750
On the other hand,

440
00:20:16,750 --> 00:20:18,210
he wanted to get Chuntiao.

441
00:20:18,430 --> 00:20:19,550
That makes sense.

442
00:20:19,910 --> 00:20:20,950
Dong Haogu kept saying

443
00:20:20,950 --> 00:20:22,550
everything he said was true.

444
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:25,310
But how can we be credulous facing such a profiteer?

445
00:20:25,310 --> 00:20:26,640
Who else do you suspect?

446
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:28,830
Niu Daming.

447
00:20:29,870 --> 00:20:30,780
The night watchman, Uncle Zhong,

448
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:31,970
saw it with his own eyes

449
00:20:31,970 --> 00:20:35,630
that he escaped from the burial goods store before 1 a.m. in panic.

450
00:20:37,320 --> 00:20:38,670
The reason why he looked flustered

451
00:20:38,670 --> 00:20:39,750
was that he just killed

452
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:40,350
Dugu Yang.

453
00:20:40,750 --> 00:20:42,230
Who is it?

454
00:20:50,390 --> 00:20:51,160
Niu Daming.

455
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:53,120
Why are you here again?

456
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:56,860
My wife's business has nothing to do with you.

457
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,670
But if you die,

458
00:21:00,190 --> 00:21:02,580
your wife will have everything to do with me.

459
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:04,630
The woman of my dream, Chuntiao,

460
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:06,790
will be mine.

461
00:21:08,270 --> 00:21:09,200
To get Chuntiao,

462
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:10,690
Niu Daming has gone crazy.

463
00:21:11,430 --> 00:21:12,430
Now I think

464
00:21:12,450 --> 00:21:14,110
we should interrogate Niu Daming first.

465
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:15,430
He's even more suspicious than Chunshan.

466
00:21:15,430 --> 00:21:15,990
Besides,

467
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,170
there's a witness.

468
00:21:17,630 --> 00:21:18,910
What you said does make sense.

469
00:21:18,910 --> 00:21:20,840
But Niu Daming refused to confess.

470
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:24,470
He has worked in the government office for many years.

471
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:25,530
He's very cunning.

472
00:21:25,990 --> 00:21:27,490
If we want him to confess,

473
00:21:28,350 --> 00:21:29,810
we'll have to torture him.

474
00:21:31,710 --> 00:21:32,790
Dugu Xiashu.

475
00:21:34,110 --> 00:21:35,510
Not long ago in Chang'an,

476
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:37,710
the Mara escaped the wall  and caused a bloodbath.

477
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:40,540
Time was tight, and there was no way to investigate.

478
00:21:40,540 --> 00:21:42,270
Some suspects were arrested.

479
00:21:43,270 --> 00:21:44,150
But Su Wuming and I

480
00:21:44,150 --> 00:21:45,870
never tortured anyone

481
00:21:48,350 --> 00:21:49,990
because we were worried that they'd confess to avoid being punished,

482
00:21:49,990 --> 00:21:52,390
which may result in wrongful convictions.

483
00:21:56,790 --> 00:21:57,670
I'm ashamed.

484
00:22:00,430 --> 00:22:02,630
Thank you for reminding me, General Lu.

485
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:05,200
So now, we...

486
00:22:05,420 --> 00:22:06,150
Lu Lingfeng.

487
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:10,490
I drew it according to Qingniao's statement.

488
00:22:15,230 --> 00:22:16,230
Magistrate Dugu.

489
00:22:16,430 --> 00:22:17,710
The judgement you made before

490
00:22:17,710 --> 00:22:18,550
is unfair.

491
00:22:19,670 --> 00:22:21,580
Why is that? Please enlighten me.

492
00:22:22,110 --> 00:22:24,030
Considering the items Dong Haogu bought from the tomb,

493
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:25,870
his crime is tantamount to tomb robbery.

494
00:22:25,870 --> 00:22:27,470
But he was only flogged 20 times

495
00:22:27,470 --> 00:22:28,800
before he was released.

496
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:31,350
Although Niu Daming stabbed someone with a dagger in the street,

497
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:33,150
it was just an attempted murder.

498
00:22:33,590 --> 00:22:35,350
Besides, he's been a government official for years.

499
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:37,350
He may have not achieved much, but he did work hard.

500
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:39,210
How could you put him on death row?

501
00:22:39,990 --> 00:22:42,230
So what's your opinion, General Lu?

502
00:22:42,260 --> 00:22:42,990
Release him.

503
00:22:43,310 --> 00:22:46,840
After all, he's worked in the government office for a long time.

504
00:22:46,910 --> 00:22:48,440
If you treat your subordinates nicely,

505
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,500
when others see it,

506
00:22:49,900 --> 00:22:52,100
they'll also be willing to work for you.

507
00:22:52,430 --> 00:22:54,170
I don't think we should do that.

508
00:22:54,190 --> 00:22:54,990
Why not?

509
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,590
I've said everything I have to say.

510
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:12,960
Why do they want me to go to court again?

511
00:23:13,790 --> 00:23:15,390
They don't want you in court.

512
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:17,190
They said you can go home now.

513
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:18,980
Zhou.

514
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:20,810
Are you kidding me?

515
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,650
Leave here or not, I don't care.

516
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:32,700
Why are you riding so fast?

517
00:23:33,190 --> 00:23:35,050
How can you ride a horse like that?

518
00:23:48,870 --> 00:23:49,750
Who did that?

519
00:23:55,190 --> 00:23:56,590
I only want the treasure.

520
00:23:57,030 --> 00:23:58,290
I don't want your life.

521
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,430
Just leave your package

522
00:24:00,950 --> 00:24:01,910
and get lost.

523
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,830
Where did you come from, little bandit?

524
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:06,090
How dare you kidnap me?

525
00:24:07,590 --> 00:24:09,350
Do you want to die?

526
00:24:34,430 --> 00:24:36,020
Hero, let's be friends.

527
00:24:36,630 --> 00:24:37,470
How about

528
00:24:38,190 --> 00:24:39,310
we share the treasure half and half?

529
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:40,170
In your dreams.

530
00:24:41,230 --> 00:24:42,690
There's a treasure called

531
00:24:42,950 --> 00:24:44,150
Dugu's seal or something.

532
00:24:44,150 --> 00:24:45,680
If you have that treasure,

533
00:24:45,990 --> 00:24:47,850
I may consider sparing your life.

534
00:24:48,020 --> 00:24:50,080
You mean Dugu Xin Multifaceted Seal?

535
00:24:50,270 --> 00:24:50,680
Yes.

536
00:24:51,070 --> 00:24:52,070
I don't have that.

537
00:24:53,270 --> 00:24:55,110
You're about to die, and you're still lying.

538
00:24:55,110 --> 00:24:55,790
Looks like

539
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:58,020
I have no option but cut off your head.

540
00:24:58,470 --> 00:24:58,950
Don't.

541
00:24:59,550 --> 00:25:00,750
I really don't have it.

542
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:01,270
Hero.

543
00:25:01,740 --> 00:25:02,940
Please spare my life.

544
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:03,770
You can have

545
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:04,480
all these.

546
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:05,640
I just want the seal.

547
00:25:05,820 --> 00:25:07,880
That seal has got many people killed.

548
00:25:07,990 --> 00:25:08,870
But until now,

549
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:10,190
no one has seen it.

550
00:25:10,590 --> 00:25:11,030
I think

551
00:25:11,430 --> 00:25:12,430
it's just a lie

552
00:25:12,470 --> 00:25:13,190
made up by Dugu Yang

553
00:25:13,190 --> 00:25:14,120
to fool his wife.

554
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:16,610
There is no such thing in the world at all.

555
00:25:16,750 --> 00:25:17,600
Unfortunately,

556
00:25:17,600 --> 00:25:20,050
I was also deceived even though I worked in the government office for years.

557
00:25:20,050 --> 00:25:21,310
I almost got beheaded.

558
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:22,490
Fortunately,

559
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:23,870
the nerd magistrate is a fool.

560
00:25:23,870 --> 00:25:24,730
He released me.

561
00:25:24,910 --> 00:25:26,910
That's why I was running for my life.

562
00:25:32,410 --> 00:25:34,140
Although I'm a nerd magistrate

563
00:25:34,270 --> 00:25:35,240
and I couldn't get my head around it,

564
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:36,170
where did you get

565
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:37,340
so many gold and jewels?

566
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:39,340
You're just a government official.

567
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:44,340
Niu Daming.

568
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:47,830
Niu Daming.

569
00:25:49,830 --> 00:25:51,920
Where is Dugu Xiashu?

570
00:25:54,190 --> 00:25:55,670
Mr. Su, you....

571
00:25:56,780 --> 00:25:57,870
You're awake.

572
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:00,790
Zhou.

573
00:26:01,870 --> 00:26:05,000
Niu Daming is very cunning.

574
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:06,670
We can release him for now

