00:39:57,670 --> 00:39:58,870
I went to his house to beg him many times.

864
00:39:58,870 --> 00:40:00,440
I bought a load of clay

865
00:40:00,590 --> 00:40:01,870
specially used for clay figurine making every month

866
00:40:01,870 --> 00:40:02,750
and sent it to him

867
00:40:02,750 --> 00:40:04,210
to show my determination.

868
00:40:04,510 --> 00:40:05,040
Finally,

869
00:40:05,670 --> 00:40:06,580
2 months ago,

870
00:40:07,070 --> 00:40:07,870
he agreed.

871
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:13,120
So you really agree?

872
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:15,950
I've thought it through.

873
00:40:16,130 --> 00:40:17,390
If I can use my craftsmanship

874
00:40:17,390 --> 00:40:18,450
to make some money,

875
00:40:19,140 --> 00:40:21,120
Chuntiao can live a better life.

876
00:40:21,870 --> 00:40:23,000
That'll be worth it.

877
00:40:25,620 --> 00:40:26,280
Master.

878
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,810
How much did you pay Dugu Yang?

879
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:30,270
We agreed

880
00:40:30,550 --> 00:40:32,680
I'd pay him 9 silver ingots of 10 taels.

881
00:40:32,750 --> 00:40:33,840
3 per month,

882
00:40:33,870 --> 00:40:34,790
for 3 months.

883
00:40:35,940 --> 00:40:37,000
I've paid 6 of them.

884
00:40:37,270 --> 00:40:38,470
There are documents.

885
00:40:41,790 --> 00:40:42,990
6 silver ingots?

886
00:40:43,830 --> 00:40:45,490
Why haven't I seen any of them?

887
00:40:48,060 --> 00:40:48,870
I asked

888
00:40:49,630 --> 00:40:50,360
Master once.

889
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:52,570
Master.

890
00:40:52,990 --> 00:40:55,650
Is your wife happy to receive the silver ingots?

891
00:40:56,070 --> 00:40:57,800
I haven't given them to her yet.

892
00:40:58,170 --> 00:40:59,630
The day you finish your apprenticeship

893
00:40:59,630 --> 00:41:01,280
happens to be Chuntiao's birthday.

894
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,720
I'll give them to her all at once when the time comes.

895
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:04,260
I'm sure she'll be happy.

896
00:41:09,470 --> 00:41:10,110
I heard

897
00:41:10,470 --> 00:41:12,870
your wife goes out to have tea and drinks with people a lot.

898
00:41:12,870 --> 00:41:13,330
Master.

899
00:41:13,790 --> 00:41:14,990
I don't want to hear

900
00:41:15,030 --> 00:41:16,760
those boring people's gossip.

901
00:41:17,390 --> 00:41:18,990
Don't you spread it, either.

902
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:23,190
She's my wife, I...

903
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:25,270
I know what kind of person she is.

904
00:41:26,070 --> 00:41:28,130
She won't do anything behind my back.

905
00:41:29,410 --> 00:41:30,510
Chuntiao.

906
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:33,450
Why are you crying in court?

907
00:41:33,790 --> 00:41:35,510
How inappropriate.

908
00:41:36,030 --> 00:41:36,580
Yes.

909
00:41:37,350 --> 00:41:37,830
Ma Huai.

910
00:41:38,360 --> 00:41:39,870
Do others know

911
00:41:40,540 --> 00:41:41,790
that you took Dugu Yang as your master?

912
00:41:41,790 --> 00:41:43,450
He asked me to keep it a secret.

913
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:46,210
I didn't want to publicize it either.

914
00:41:47,270 --> 00:41:48,070
In that case,

915
00:41:48,430 --> 00:41:49,800
the silver ingots Qingniao saw that day,

916
00:41:49,800 --> 00:41:51,330
which you gave to Dugu Yang,

917
00:41:51,540 --> 00:41:53,630
were the fee for your apprenticeship.

918
00:41:53,630 --> 00:41:54,070
Yes.

919
00:41:54,830 --> 00:41:55,630
A few days ago,

920
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:57,510
I completed 2 months of apprenticeship.

921
00:41:57,510 --> 00:41:58,910
Now that I think about it,

922
00:41:59,550 --> 00:42:00,070
that day

923
00:42:00,910 --> 00:42:01,630
was the day

924
00:42:01,630 --> 00:42:03,760
when Master examined Lou Lide's body.

925
00:42:05,230 --> 00:42:06,310
Lou Lide?

926
00:42:07,470 --> 00:42:08,470
The executioner?

927
00:42:09,350 --> 00:42:10,950
I examined his body.

928
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:18,430
There are no injuries on the skin

929
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,590
and no signs of poisoning.

930
00:42:21,030 --> 00:42:22,750
He should have died of an acute disease.

931
00:42:22,750 --> 00:42:24,220
He had no facial nerve paralysis

932
00:42:24,220 --> 00:42:25,620
or limb paralysis.

933
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:27,270
So it wasn't a stroke.

934
00:42:27,830 --> 00:42:29,310
He seems to be in pain.

935
00:42:30,070 --> 00:42:32,070
It should be that his chest got pinched,

936
00:42:32,070 --> 00:42:34,600
and he died of chest tightness and chest pain.

937
00:42:35,390 --> 00:42:36,120
This disease

938
00:42:36,740 --> 00:42:38,430
is also known as angina.

939
00:42:39,270 --> 00:42:41,750
It often occurs when a person uses a lot of energy

940
00:42:41,750 --> 00:42:44,060
after he overeats.

941
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:45,870
In this case, he ate

942
00:42:45,910 --> 00:42:48,830
too many naans stuffed with lamb.

943
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:50,070
After that,

944
00:42:50,100 --> 00:42:52,090
he started lifting stone padlocks in the yard

945
00:42:52,090 --> 00:42:53,630
to exercise his arm strength.

946
00:42:53,630 --> 00:42:55,070
That's right.

947
00:42:55,630 --> 00:42:56,430
Son,

948
00:42:57,110 --> 00:42:59,440
the result of your postmortem is correct.

949
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:06,830
It's good to have you to double check, Mother.

950
00:43:08,870 --> 00:43:10,950
I've been a coroner all my life,

951
00:43:11,020 --> 00:43:13,180
and I never made any mistake.

952
00:43:13,670 --> 00:43:14,790
I didn't

953
00:43:14,990 --> 00:43:16,550
do the techniques you taught me wrong

954
00:43:16,550 --> 00:43:18,630
or let you down, Mother.

955
00:43:20,030 --> 00:43:20,870
My son.

956
00:43:21,790 --> 00:43:22,880
What's wrong?

957
00:43:23,390 --> 00:43:24,590
You're so young.

958
00:43:24,910 --> 00:43:27,150
Why did you say things like "all your life"?

959
00:43:27,150 --> 00:43:27,980
Mother.

960
00:43:29,990 --> 00:43:31,510
My greatest blessing

961
00:43:32,150 --> 00:43:34,270
is to be your son.

962
00:43:35,320 --> 00:43:37,580
You no longer regret becoming a coroner?

963
00:43:43,070 --> 00:43:47,060
It's a low-paid and menial job.

964
00:43:47,990 --> 00:43:49,350
But the job of a coroner

965
00:43:50,030 --> 00:43:52,150
is a matter of the truth of death

966
00:43:52,190 --> 00:43:53,790
and the justice in the world.

967
00:43:55,930 --> 00:43:57,360
Someone has to do it.

968
00:44:05,310 --> 00:44:05,830
Ma Huai.

969
00:44:06,190 --> 00:44:07,000
In that case,

970
00:44:07,050 --> 00:44:08,230
you are actually a nice person.

971
00:44:08,230 --> 00:44:10,350
But you strangled Lou Qingtai to death.

972
00:44:10,350 --> 00:44:11,840
It's a capital crime.
